data.description: Charming custom home in desirable South La Grande. Light and bright open floor plan. This 4 bed 2.5 bath features primary suit on main floor, outstanding kitchen with endless storage, cozy gas fireplace with hardwood floors. Energy efficient radiant heat throughout supported by new boiler. Multiple decks lead to your private in town getaway backyard that is fully fenced. Converted, detached garage that allows for many possibilities. This turnkey home is a must see
